  <brief_title>Comparison of Traditional Superficial Cutaneous Sutures Versus Steri-Strip Coaptive Film in Layered Dermatologic Closures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Traditional Superficial Cutaneous Sutures Versus Steri-Strip Coaptive Film in Layered Dermatologic Closures on the Back - a Prospective, Randomized, Split-scar Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
