  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the cosmetic outcome between buried intradermal and
      superficial cutaneous suture closures versus buried intradermal sutureand superficial
      Steri-Strip closures in the bilayered repair of dermatologic wounds on the back following
      elliptical excision of benign or malignant lesions
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
